---
import MarketingLayout from '../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro';

const appUrl = 'https://app.getanswerlayer.com';
const docsUrl = 'https://docs.getanswerlayer.com';
---

<MarketingLayout
  title="AnswerLayer - Secure Context Layer for Analytics Agents"
  description="Transform your data into actionable insights with the power of AI. Agentic insights in your products. Conversational analytics for internal business intelligence."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section
    class="min-h-[calc(100vh-80px)] pt-20 flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden"
    style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)), url('/hero_bg.png'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; background-repeat: no-repeat;"
  >
    <!-- Animated overlay elements -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute -top-1/2 -right-1/2 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-100/10 to-transparent rounded-full animate-parallax-float"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-1/2 -left-1/2 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-blue-100/10 to-transparent rounded-full animate-parallax-float" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-custom relative z-10 text-center">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-serif font-light mb-8 leading-tight tracking-wide text-navy-900">
          Secure, <span class="italic text-navy-600">reliable</span> context layer for analytics agents.
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed">
          Agentic insights in your products. <br />
          Conversational analytics for internal business intelligence.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center mb-16">
          <a
            href={`${appUrl}/sign-up?redirect=connections%2Fnew`}
            class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"
          >
            Get Answers
            <svg class="ml-2 h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
              <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </a>

          <a
            href={docsUrl}
            class="btn btn-outline btn-lg"
          >
            Build Your Agents
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="animate-bounce">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-navy-400 mx-auto" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Vision Section -->
  <section id="vision-section" class="py-32 bg-white relative">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-light mb-8 text-navy-900">
          The Age of <span class="italic">Intelligent</span> Data
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed">
          Data is still too often locked away behind technical barriers.
          SQL, schemas, pipelines. All necessary, but not sufficient.
          Decisions are driven by systems that understand both data and intent.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="border-l-4 border-red-300 pl-6">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-3 text-gray-900">The Current Way</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Messy data. Expensive pipelines. Weeks to insights. Static dashboards. Business questions lost in translation.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="border-l-4 border-navy-500 pl-6">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-3 text-navy-900">With AnswerLayer</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Agents meet data where it is, as it is. Conversations replace queries. Insight flows freely.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-50 to-blue-100 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-navy-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path d="M12 2a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v1a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H8a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V9a2 2 0 0 1 2-2V6a4 4 0 0 1 4-4z"></path>
                    <circle cx="12" cy="18" r="4"></circle>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-sm font-medium">AI Agent</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">"Why is the Q2 cohort retaining at a higher rate than Q1?"</p>
              </div>

              <div class="flex justify-center">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-navy-400" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
                  <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
                </svg>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-navy-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"></ellipse>
                    <path d="M3 5V19A9 3 0 0 0 21 19V5"></path>
                    <path d="M3 12A9 3 0 0 0 21 12"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-sm font-medium">AnswerLayer</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Semantic understanding + optimized query</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Four Pillars Section -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-light mb-6 text-navy-900">
          Four Pillars of <span class="italic">Intelligent</span> Data
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light">
          We've built the foundational layer that makes AI and data work together seamlessly.
          Here's how we're reshaping the landscape.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- Pillar 1: API for AI Agents -->
        <div class="group">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-navy-200 transition-colors">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-navy-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline>
                  <polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-navy-900">API for AI Agents</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Every AI agent needs data. We make databases speak their language.
              RESTful endpoints that understand context, intent, and deliver exactly what intelligence systems need.
            </p>
            <div class="text-sm text-navy-600 font-medium">
              Natural language -> Structured queries -> Agent-ready responses
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pillar 2: Semantic Layer -->
        <div class="group">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-navy-200 transition-colors">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-navy-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M12 2a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v1a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H8a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V9a2 2 0 0 1 2-2V6a4 4 0 0 1 4-4z"></path>
                  <circle cx="12" cy="18" r="4"></circle>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-navy-900">Semantic Layer</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Business language becomes standard, repeatable metrics.
              "Revenue" means the same thing across every query, every agent, every conversation.
            </p>
            <div class="text-sm text-navy-600 font-medium">
              Business concepts -> Consistent definitions -> Universal understanding
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pillar 3: Hybrid Intelligence -->
        <div class="group">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-navy-200 transition-colors">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-navy-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"></polygon>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-navy-900">Hybrid Intelligence</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Traditional databases + LLM reasoning = unstoppable insights.
              We bridge the gap between structured data and intelligent interpretation.
            </p>
            <div class="text-sm text-navy-600 font-medium">
              Proven infrastructure + AI reasoning -> Reliable intelligence
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pillar 4: AI Analyst -->
        <div class="group">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-navy-200 transition-colors">
                <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-navy-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
                  <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
                  <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
                  <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-navy-900">AI Analyst</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Your internal BI gets super powers.
              Every team member becomes a data expert, limited only by the sophistication of their questions.
            </p>
            <div class="text-sm text-navy-600 font-medium">
              Natural questions -> Deep analysis -> Actionable insights
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom text-center">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-light mb-8 text-navy-900">
          Ready to Get <span class="italic">Answers?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12 font-light">
          Your data is ready. Join the companies already building the future of intelligent data.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
          <a
            href={`${appUrl}/sign-up?redirect=connections%2Fnew`}
            class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"
          >
            Get Started
            <svg class="ml-2 h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
              <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-8">
          No credit card required &bull; 5-minute setup &bull; Enterprise ready
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MarketingLayout>
